cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.DS

This paper proposes a new meta-heuristic algorithm for optimization problems. The algorithm combines swarm intelligence and feedback-based step-size update strategy. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
